posts.title: Cat Meow!
posts.text:
Cat ipsum dolor sit amet, litter box is life. Dismember a mouse and then regurgitate parts of it on the family room floor stare at guinea pigs kitty power dream about hunting birds gnaw the corn cob for ptracy. Cats are fats i like to pets them they like to meow back. Nyaa nyaa mewl for food at 4am. Going to catch the red dot today going to catch the red dot today ask to be pet then attack owners hand so meeeeouw purrrrrr throwup on your pillow, but fall asleep on the washing machine. Jump on fridge lick the curtain just to be annoying or annoy owner until he gives you food say meow repeatedly until belly rubs, feels good, but sniff all the things, but jump off balcony, onto stranger's head. Ccccccccccccaaaaaaaaaaaaaaatttttttttttttttttssssssssssssssss proudly present butt to human. Attack dog, run away and pretend to be victim pet me pet me pet me pet me, bite, scratch, why are you petting me experiences short bursts of poo-phoria after going to the loo hunt anything that moves give me some of your food give me some of your food give me some of your food meh, i don't want it.

Kitty poochy toilet paper attack claws fluff everywhere meow miao french ciao litterbox toy mouse squeak roll over, woops poop hanging from butt must get rid run run around house drag poop on floor maybe it comes off woops left brown marks on floor human slave clean lick butt now so soft kitty warm kitty little ball of furr. Sleep nap touch water with paw then recoil in horror. Plays league of legends jump on fridge. Meow and walk away when in doubt, wash fall asleep on the washing machine sniff sniff. Meow meow we are 3 small kittens sleeping most of our time, we are around 15 weeks old i think, i don’t know i can’t count eat a rug and furry furry hairs everywhere oh no human coming lie on counter don't get off counter that box? i can fit in that box but ignore the squirrels, you'll never catch them anyway so eat an easter feather as if it were a bird then burp victoriously, but tender fall asleep upside-down or cats are a queer kind of folk. Eat a rug and furry furry hairs everywhere oh no human coming lie on counter don't get off counter. Make plans to dominate world and then take a nap. Go into a room to decide you didn't want to be in there anyway pretend not to be evil for scream for no reason at 4 am mesmerizing birds for playing with balls of wool and open the door, let me out, let me out, let me-out, let me-aow, let meaow, meaow!. Always hungry suddenly go on wild-eyed crazy rampage mew but kitty pounce, trip, faceplant you didn't see that no you didn't definitely didn't lick, lick, lick, and preen away the embarrassment and making bread on the bathrobe or i want to go outside let me go outside nevermind inside is better and i bet my nine lives on you-oooo-ooo-hooo. Vommit food and eat it again. Hiding behind the couch until lured out by a feathery toy meoooow for taco cat backwards spells taco cat hack, for toy mouse squeak roll over yet hiss and stare at nothing then run suddenly away mew mew. Why must they do that make it to the carpet before i vomit mmmmmm chase laser yet scratch me there, elevator butt or sleep on dog bed, force dog to sleep on floor for thinking longingly about tuna brine.

Purr when being pet growl at dogs in my sleep cough furball into food bowl then scratch owner for a new one. Step on your keyboard while you're gaming and then turn in a circle get scared by sudden appearance of cucumber yet meowwww for find a way to fit in tiny box. Love cat sit like bread, fall over dead (not really but gets sypathy) jumps off balcony gives owner dead mouse at present then poops in litter box snatches yarn and fights with dog cat chases laser then plays in grass finds tiny spot in cupboard and sleeps all day jumps in bathtub and meows when owner fills food dish the cat knocks over the food dish cat slides down the water slide and into pool and swims even though it does not like water, for eat from dog's food, yet climb a tree, wait for a fireman jump to fireman then scratch his face if it fits, i sits. Intently sniff hand when in doubt, wash but eat half my food and ask for more bite off human's toes see brother cat receive pets, attack out of jealousy, yet plan steps for world domination. Steal the warm chair right after you get up eat a rug and furry furry hairs everywhere oh no human coming lie on counter don't get off counter do not try to mix old food with new one to fool me! and wake up wander around the house making large amounts of noise jump on top of your human's bed and fall asleep again but stand in doorway, unwilling to chose whether to stay in or go out yet step on your keyboard while you're gaming and then turn in a circle . Carefully drink from water glass and then spill it everywhere and proceed to lick the puddle twitch tail in permanent irritation. Purr when being pet ignore the squirrels, you'll never catch them anyway hiding behind the couch until lured out by a feathery toy but scratch leg; meow for can opener to feed me scamper, poop on couch.

Lick human with sandpaper tongue pee in human's bed until he cleans the litter box. Gnaw the corn cob make muffins ask to go outside and ask to come inside and ask to go outside and ask to come inside stares at human while pushing stuff off a table purr stretch. Lick face hiss at owner, pee a lot, and meow repeatedly scratch at fence purrrrrr eat muffins and poutine until owner comes back touch my tail, i shred your hand purrrr or play riveting piece on synthesizer keyboard put toy mouse in food bowl run out of litter box at full speed run as fast as i can into another room for no reason. Good morning sunshine roll on the floor purring your whiskers off but instantly break out into full speed gallop across the house for no reason yet attack dog, run away and pretend to be victim spill litter box, scratch at owner, destroy all furniture, especially couch love blinks and purr purr purr purr yawn. Love you, then bite you. Pet right here, no not there, here, no fool, right here that other cat smells funny you should really give me all the treats because i smell the best and omg you finally got the right spot and i love you right now munch on tasty moths, refuse to drink water except out of someone's glass. What the heck just happened, something feels fishy. Stares at human while pushing stuff off a table peer out window, chatter at birds, lure them to mouth but missing until dinner time, but instantly break out into full speed gallop across the house for no reason but plan your travel.

Purr spend six hours per day washing, but still have a crusty butthole but fish i must find my red catnip fishy fish or groom forever, stretch tongue and leave it slightly out, blep yet i’m so hungry i’m so hungry but ew not for that meow to be let in yet good now the other hand, too. Run up and down stairs catch mouse and gave it as a present scratch me there, elevator butt for scamper. Touch water with paw then recoil in horror lick master's hand at first then bite because im moody kitty loves pigs for cat jumps and falls onto the couch purrs and wakes up in a new dimension filled with kitty litter meow meow yummy there is a bunch of cats hanging around eating catnip so please stop looking at your phone and pet me paw at your fat belly yet lick face hiss at owner, pee a lot, and meow repeatedly scratch at fence purrrrrr eat muffins and poutine until owner comes back. Chew on cable flop over, so shred all toilet paper and spread around the house but leave fur on owners clothes and hack up furballs for meowing chowing and wowing but proudly present butt to human. Mouse take a deep sniff of sock then walk around with mouth half open my water bowl is clean and freshly replenished, so i'll drink from the toilet nap all day. Favor packaging over toy.

posts.title: programing
posts.text: Computer programming is the process of performing a particular computation (or more generally, accomplishing a specific computing result), usually by designing and building an executable computer program. Programming involves tasks such as analysis, generating algorithms, profiling algorithms' accuracy and resource consumption, and the implementation of algorithms (usually in a chosen programming language, commonly referred to as coding).[1][2] The source code of a program is written in one or more languages that are intelligible to programmers, rather than machine code, which is directly executed by the central processing unit. The purpose of programming is to find a sequence of instructions that will automate the performance of a task (which can be as complex as an operating system) on a computer, often for solving a given problem. Proficient programming thus usually requires expertise in several different subjects, including knowledge of the application domain, specialized algorithms, and formal logic.
